{"id": "1361260947083235470", "channel_id": "1361260947083235470", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：艾瑞卡EP·機械之心，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：艾瑞卡EP·機械之心\n在她成為冰冷的機械前，也曾有過鮮活的靈魂。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Erica EP·Mechanical Heart》 was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Erica EP·Mechanical Heart》 \nBefore she became a cold machine, she had a vibrant soul.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-04-14T08:45:00.790000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "⚙️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1361260947569905804", "filename": "OST-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1829458, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1361260947083235470/1361260947569905804/OST-.jpg?ex=69ccdb0c&is=69cb898c&hm=cb2c089d3aaf4e60c983b38650e68e408fcb04f57e72cf5a26fa9b99409e09cc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1361260947083235470", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：艾瑞卡EP·機械之心", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1361261337094782976", "channel_id": "1361260947083235470", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.天才的煩惱-Prodigy's Faux Pas-**\n\n天才的腦迴路總有那麼一些蜿蜒、曲折、與眾不同，但那正是她的可愛之處，不是嗎？\nThe brain circuits of geniuses are always a bit winding, twisted, and unique, but that is what makes her lovely, isn't it?", "timestamp": "2025-04-14T08:46:33.776000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1361261336595664896", "filename": "1.-Prodigys_Faux_Pas-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19625146, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1361260947083235470/1361261336595664896/1.-Prodigys_Faux_Pas-.wav?ex=69ccdb69&is=69cb89e9&hm=b818837248eda2604e23f3f05c9fc147de29c7aab7e43fb784f048afd7fcf95d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1361260947083235470", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：艾瑞卡EP·機械之心", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1361261433811243019", "channel_id": "1361260947083235470", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.孤獨救援-Solitary Rescue-**\n\n她的靈魂在你身後，你一人即是此刻唯一的城牆，而命運的無力感將你牢牢俘獲，你改變不了那個結局。\n那個她被黑色潮水淹沒的結局。\nHer soul is behind you, and you are the only wall at this moment, and the powerlessness of fate has captured you firmly, and you cannot change the ending.\nThe ending where she was submerged by the black tide.", "timestamp": "2025-04-14T08:46:56.835000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1361261433408454759", "filename": "2.-Solitary_Rescue-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 28549558, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1361260947083235470/1361261433408454759/2.-Solitary_Rescue-.wav?ex=69ccdb80&is=69cb8a00&hm=b819d30cc5754f9bf1e5f8c9d3bcc366d4472362e72751d13ae66aeffdc60476&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1361260947083235470", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：艾瑞卡EP·機械之心", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
